## 💬 Questions and Help
I have problem with reading data validation when it was Excel Reference in different sheets. (I could read, if rangee is in same sheet)

My use case is : I created an Excel sheet with all kind of validations. I could get other type of data validation but when definition like below it is not possible. 

Are there anybody lived same problem and solved it?

Thank you.

worksheet.getCell('A1').dataValidation = {
  type: 'list',
  allowBlank: true,
  formulae: ['$D$5:$F$5'] -->  Sheet2!$D$3:$D$7 
